# Project Governance

Before writing any code, read the rules in `rules/`:

- `rules/README.md` — index
- `rules/folder-structure.md` — where files go
- `rules/code-reuse.md` — no duplicate logic
- `rules/documentation.md` — update `output/TASKS.md` for every task

**Build gate:** No `apps/` code without a task doc in `output/`. Move task files between `pending/`, `in-progress/`, `completed/` and update `output/TASKS.md`.
